{"tid":2451718,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"陸榮廷睇相  唔衰拿來衰","createTime":"2021-03-18T09:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T04:01:46.000Z","uid":258784,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e14d1fd7783cf4deb5e89b227f5c38ce7610d95","tid":2451718,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"2021版：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">葉國謙駁嘴  自己攞嚟柒</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><ins>原典故：</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n陸榮廷，廣西舊桂系軍閥，兩次粵桂戰爭期間曾經一度控制廣東。關於陸榮廷睇相嘅傳說有幾種版本，以下採用一種最常見嘅版本：陸榮廷擔任兩廣巡閱使嘅時候，有一日，佢突然想攗個相士同自己睇相，但係又驚被個相士睇出自己係達官貴人。於是佢攗咗套窮人嘅爛衫褲，著起身，扮成窮人去攗相士睇相。偏偏個相士又真係睇出咗伊個扮成窮人來睇相嘅係陸榮廷，於是就特登講：「阿貴生原本就好有富貴相嘅，不過阿貴生特登著到成個窮人恁樣，就真係『唔衰拿來衰』囉。」結果無幾耐，1921年，陸榮廷嘅勢力就被孫中山同陳炯明打敗，被逼退出廣東。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">摘自：<a href=\"https://yue.m.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E9%99%B8%E6%A6%AE%E5%BB%B7%E7%9D%87%E7%9B%B8%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%94%94%E8%A1%B0%E6%8B%BF%E4%BE%86%E8%A1%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyue.m.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2599%25B8%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%259B%25B8%25E2%2580%2594%25E2%2580%2594%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25A1%25B0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A1%25B0&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2fFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=70743200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yue.m.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E9%99%B8%E6%A6%AE%E5%BB%B7%E7%9D%87%E7%9B%B8%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%94%94%E8%A1%B0%E6%8B%BF%E4%BE%86%E8%A1%B0</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins>新典故</ins></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2021年嘅3月，中共官員田飛龍公開話建制派中存在「忠誠廢物」，表達對建制派過往辦事不力，Hea住做嘅不滿。本來田飛龍冇指名道姓，件事亦都冇引發太大迴響，已經告一段落，點知葉國謙對號入座，仲高調駁嘴話返田飛龍係廢柴學者。咁爆嘅言論就觸怒咗田飛龍，田飛龍焗住回應葉國謙提到「忠誠廢物」係一個現象而咁係淨係指某啲人，暗示建制派全部都係垃圾。第二日田飛龍再補充話建制派確實係「忠誠廢物」，仲話佢哋唔適合服務香港同國家。<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K82ocG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK82ocG2.jpg&h=7ab0095e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/symkeVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsymkeVs.jpg&h=2f80490b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0x7Ena.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0x7Ena.jpg&h=8f220a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6EaB8V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6EaB8V.png&h=e92ffcfe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9de02cbf3be6f82b168e9844c2c5e81de0c9801","tid":2451718,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42176af8a61da1096c53cdaa6669cf7ad2882a44","tid":2451718,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"以後大家可以用葉國謙駁嘴嚟代替「陸榮廷睇相」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a377abc8c2b495e699df5e2d566d3dcc1492d636","tid":2451718,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"拍馬屁拍著馬春袋"},{"pid":"96378b719c8af90d3376da932534959b1371c055","tid":2451718,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b9a50875c2e9dbdfbd567435454c4bf9f934a4","tid":2451718,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96378b719c8af90d3376da932534959b1371c055","